# 007 - API keys (easy to edit). Throwaway / short-lived keys are fine here.
#
# How to use: remove the "#" at the start of a line and paste your key after "=".
# Lines starting with "#" and blank lines are ignored. No quotes needed.
# This file is read automatically when you run 007.py.
# Real environment variables (if set) take precedence over this file.
# It is git-ignored, so the keys you put here are NOT pushed to GitHub.

# ---------- Free / free-tier providers ----------
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
# CEREBRAS_API_KEY=csk-...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
# OLLAMA_API_KEY=...          # Ollama Cloud (provider: ollama-cloud). Local ollama needs no key.

# ---------- Paid providers ----------
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# MISTRAL_API_KEY=...
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...
